name: X-MEN Archives Artist Proof Sketch Card: Rogue Storm Psylocke
description:
This is a Official Hand Drawn Uncut AP Sketch Card. This collectible one of a kind card features the the Marvel comic characters Storm, Psylocke, and Rogue.

Sketch cards are usually 2.5 x 3.5 but because this is a artist proof the Art receives the card in its uncut for and can utilize drawing on a bigger drawing area. 

Media is PrismaColor and Copic Marker and color pencil.

Shipping on this item is free but if you are interested in insurance or delivery confirmation there is an additional charge.
